Class Manifest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jayway.maven.plugins.android.configuration.Manifest

  • public class Manifest
extends Object
    Configuration for the manifest update. This class is only the definition of the parameters that are shadowed in ManifestUpdateMojo and used there.

    Manfred Moser
